Foundry VTT Module to expose some core 5e settings such there values can be editted.

Currently you can edit:
Spell Critical Fail Threshold
Weapon Critical Fail Threshold
Descriptions on Inline Rolls
Automatic Sneak Attack Rolls

Installation
--------------
Go to Foundry VTT's "Add-On Module" tab
Click "Install Module"
Paste "https://github.com/colton-howe/5e-settings/releases/latest/download/module.json" into the manifest URL
Hit Install

Directory Structure
# Templates - HTML Files
# Scripts - JS Files
# Styles - CSS Files
# Packs - Compendium Content
# Lang - Language & translations Files

